Package: inyokaedit
Architecture: any
Depends:
   ${shlibs:Depends},
   ${misc:Depends},
   wget
Suggests:
   inyokaedit-plugins,
   inyokaedit-data-ubuntuusersde,
   fonts-liberation,
   python-pygments
Description: Editor for Inyoka based portals
 InyokaEdit provides offline support for Inyoka based portals like
 ubuntuusers.de.
 .
 Features:
  * code highlighting (via plugin)
  * code completion
  * offline article preview

Package: inyokaedit-plugins
Architecture: any
Depends:
   ${shlibs:Depends},
   ${misc:Depends},
   inyokaedit (= ${binary:Version})
Suggests: hunspell
Description: Plugins for Inyokaedit
 InyokaEdit provides offline support for Inyoka based portals like
 ubuntuusers.de.
 .
 This package will install the following plugins:
  * knowledgebox
  * spellchecker
  * tabletemplate
  * syntax highlighter
  * hotkeys

Package: inyokaedit-data-ubuntuusersde
Architecture: any
Depends:
   ${shlibs:Depends},
   ${misc:Depends},
   inyokaedit (= ${binary:Version})
Description: ubuntuusers.de community files for InyokaEdit
 InyokaEdit provides offline support for Inyoka based portals like
 ubuntuusers.de.
 .
 This package will install Inyoka community files for ubuntuusers.de
